@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### GET /context — c.set / c.get (injectRequestId middleware)
GET {{baseUrl}}/context

###

### GET /users/:id — c.param / c.paramInt
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/7

###

### GET /search — c.query / c.queryInt
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=hello&page=3

###

### POST /echo — c.body
POST {{baseUrl}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "hello Darto",
  "value": 42
}

###

### GET /whoami — c.header, c.req.method, c.req.path, c.req.ip
GET {{baseUrl}}/whoami
User-Agent: api.http-client
